summary: whatever you do, dont think about Dan going out to coffee with his team, scoffing at the napkin, deciding you know what will be...
body:
whatever you do, dont think about Dan going out to coffee with his team, scoffing at the napkin, deciding you know what will be funny?

Dan placing that stupid napkin behind his sunglasses and taking a stupid selfie, his team, his friends groaning and snorting and giggling as he posts it confidently to twitter

Dan, who swore up and down that he didn’t have any friends, Dan, who was severely bullied in school, Dan, who was always silly but carefully silly, cracking jokes and peeking up through his fringe as he laughed, just to make sure others did too, Dan who doesn’t have a fringe to hide behind anymore

Dan who makes his own rules

don’t think about it too much
